1. bin/:
	build system artifacts (autotools scripts etc.)
2. m4/:
	m4 scripts.
3. docs/:
	documentation.
4. lib/:
	libraries built

5. include/:
	headers.
6. src/:
	source code.
	3) gbm/ => libgbm.so 
	   generic buffer management.
	1) egl/
	   1' main/ => libEGL.[la, so] 
	      main EGL code. 
	   2' wayland/
	      EGL wayland platform
	   3' drivers/
	   4' docs/
	5) glsl/
	   GLSL compiler(builtin)
	6) glx/ => libGL.so
	8) mapi/
	   1' es1api/ => libGLESv1_CM.so 
	   2' es2api/ => libGLESv2.so
	   3' glapi/
	   4' mapi/
	   5' shared-glapi/ => libglapi.so
	   6' vgapi/  => libOpenVG.so
	2) gallium/
	   LLVM-based Gallium drivers
	9) mesa/
	   Quite complex

	4) getopt/	: Glibc option parsing.
	7) gtest/	: Google Test Framework 
